<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Appointment Reminder</title>
  <style>
    body { margin: 0; padding: 0; font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f5; }
    .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #ffffff; }
    .header { background: linear-gradient(135deg, #0c4a6e 0%, #0369a1 100%); color: #ffffff; padding: 40px 30px; text-align: center; }
    .header h1 { margin: 0; font-size: 28px; font-weight: 600; }
    .content { padding: 40px 30px; }
    .content h2 { color: #0c4a6e; margin: 0 0 20px; font-size: 24px; }
    .content p { color: #4b5563; line-height: 1.6; margin: 0 0 16px; }
    .appointment-card { background: #f0f9ff; border: 1px solid #bae6fd; border-radius: 12px; padding: 24px; margin: 24px 0; }
    .appointment-card h3 { color: #0c4a6e; margin: 0 0 16px; font-size: 18px; }
    .appointment-detail { display: flex; margin-bottom: 12px; }
    .appointment-detail .icon { width: 24px; margin-right: 12px; color: #0284c7; }
    .appointment-detail .text { color: #374151; }
    .button { display: inline-block; padding: 14px 28px; background: #0284c7; color: #ffffff !important; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 8px; font-weight: 600; }
    .footer { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb; }
    .footer p { color: #9ca3af; font-size: 12px; margin: 0 0 8px; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>üìÖ Appointment Reminder</h1>
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      <h2>Your appointment is coming up!</h2>

      <p>Hi {{firstName}},</p>
      <p>This is a friendly reminder about your upcoming appointment:</p>

      <div class="appointment-card">
        <h3>{{serviceName}}</h3>
        <div class="appointment-detail">
          <span class="icon">üìÖ</span>
          <span class="text"><strong>Date:</strong> {{appointmentDate}}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="appointment-detail">
          <span class="icon">üïê</span>
          <span class="text"><strong>Time:</strong> {{appointmentTime}}</span>
        </div>
        {{#if location}}
        <div class="appointment-detail">
          <span class="icon">üìç</span>
          <span class="text"><strong>Location:</strong> {{location}}</span>
        </div>
        {{/if}}
      </div>

      <p>Please make sure to arrive on time. If you need to reschedule or cancel, please do so at least 24 hours in advance.</p>

      <p>
        <a href="{{appUrl}}/appointments" class="button">View My Appointments</a>
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      <p>&copy; {{year}} Memento Mori. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>We look forward to seeing you!</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

